  "schema:name": "Level 2 Calibrated 4X Reflectance Images of Sample in Tray A1",
  "schema:description": "This bundle includes calibrated images taken by the Quantitative Reflectance Imaging System (QRIS) of bulk sample moved from the TAGSAM into Tray A1. We use a 50 mm focal length lens that achieves ~4X magnification. There are 18 images total, including TIFF and PNG images of the sample under all 9 LED wavelength bands. Violet, deep red, and infrared images are taken at seperate focus settings. All images are registered to the green image.",
